narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Find the correct wording for a correct message delivery.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I liked how the course was planned but maybe having to write other writing styles apart from application essays could be a great opportunity to understand our own style.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would strongly recommend it. I think that every little advice or suggestion one receives is an opportunity for self-development and improvement.

narratives.question_text: The Canvas course site allowed me to identify and access required course materials easily.

comments: Throughout the rest if my academic years by being careful with the words i use and how to make these more effective.
